works.complaint:
We have reviews on the URL indicated which were posted
 
in 2008 and 2009. The Inchcolm Hotel has undergone massive refurbishment  

and change of management and the reviews written in 08 an 09 whilst  
probably accurate and certainly not now.
Given all our hard work and enormous investment in the property I am  
hopeful that those old reviews can be taken down. They are so far from  
relevant now and are quite distressing.
Thank you for your consideration.
Liz Martin
GENERAL MANAGER
